</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>電腦直接玩 Android 遊戲官方工具，香港 Google Play Games 測試版申請方法</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/01/20/google-play-games-for-pc-which-brings-android-games-to-windows-enters-beta-testing/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=google-play-games-for-pc-which-brings-android-games-to-windows-enters-beta-testing</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 20 Jan 2022 10:23:09 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Play Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[PC]]></category><category><![CDATA[windows]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1082077</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Google 去年曾於 The Game Awards 2021 頒獎典禮期間宣佈將在 2022 年把 And [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Google 去年曾於 The Game Awards 2021 頒獎典禮期間宣佈將在 2022 年把 Android 遊戲引入 Windows PC，今日 Google 就宣佈推出測試版，香港用戶亦可率先<a href="https://play.google.com/web/googleplaygames?pcampaignid=PR-Global-oo-gpgbeta-DevBlog">登記</a>，在開放時參與測試。參與測試的玩家可在 Windows 電腦遊玩 Google Play 的精選遊戲，已確定將搶先在香港、台灣與南韓開放。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1082078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F29CA813-6324-496A-9FF2-59885A6DDC06-694x388.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F29CA813-6324-496A-9FF2-59885A6DDC06-694x388.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F29CA813-6324-496A-9FF2-59885A6DDC06-1280x715.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F29CA813-6324-496A-9FF2-59885A6DDC06-768x429.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F29CA813-6324-496A-9FF2-59885A6DDC06.jpeg 1375w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Google 發言人 Alex Garcia-Kummert 表示，Google Play Games 應用程式讓玩家可以在更多設備上體驗最喜歡的遊戲，無論是在手機、平板、Chromebook，還是在 Windows PC 電腦上都能無縫切換，遊玩 Android 平台的各式大作。現時首輪上架的遊戲包括《無盡對決》（Mobile Legends)、《魔靈召喚》（Summoners War）、《生存防禦戰》（State of Survival）、《三國志：戰略版》 （Three Kingdoms Tactics）等；在宣傳片段中可見，估計賽車遊戲《狂野飆車 9：競速傳奇》（ASPHALT 9: LEGENDS）與《萌龍大亂鬥》（Dragon Mania Legends）未來亦將陸續上架。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1082079" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F-694x399.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="399" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F-694x399.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F-1280x737.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F-768x442.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F-1536x884.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F-2048x1178.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/F54B8BB5-9FE6-4E2E-A7B9-343199ABB90F.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據稱，Windows 用家將可透過滑鼠鍵盤來進行遊玩，並能透過該平台達成手機、平板、Chromebook 與 Windows 系統之間的同步。官方早前亦列出了最低的軟硬體需求，包括 Windows 10 (v2004)、固態硬碟 (SSD)、遊戲級 GPU、8 邏輯核心 CPU、8 GB RAM、20 GB 的可用儲存空間、Windows 管理員帳戶、必須開啟硬體虛擬化功能，及相容的電腦裝置和設定。</span></p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_29834"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TqkKjtp34Jg?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2022/01/19/google-play-games-for-pc-which-brings-android-games-to-windows-enters-beta-testing/">TechCrunch</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
